## 5. Defect log

Defects are tracked in `.sdlc/defect-log.md`.

Severity definitions:
| Severity | Criteria | Release impact |
|---|---|---|
| Critical | Data loss, security breach, complete feature failure | Block release |
| High | Major feature broken, no workaround | Block release |
| Medium | Feature impaired, workaround exists | Fix next sprint |
| Low | Minor UI / cosmetic | Fix when convenient |

---

## 6. Release sign-off criteria

Before production deployment:
- [ ] All Critical and High test cases pass
- [ ] No open Critical or High defects
- [ ] Negative test cases executed for all features in scope
- [ ] Regression suite passes: `{{TEST_CMD}}`
- [ ] Performance baseline within acceptable range
- [ ] Security spot-check completed

